# Test Configuration for Simultaneous Timeline Execution
# This tests the fix for simultaneous entries at the same timestamp
#
# Format: time frequency duty brightness channel (for LED)
#         A time frequency pan volume modulation channel (for Audio)

# Test 1: Simultaneous entries at t=0 (start of timeline)
0 20 50 100 1                 # LED: Start 20Hz white flicker
A 0 400 -100 70 0 0           # Audio Left: 400Hz tone
A 0 420 100 70 0 1            # Audio Right: 420Hz tone (creates 20Hz binaural beat)

# Test 2: Simultaneous entries at t=2000ms
2000 8 50 75 1                # LED: Change to 8Hz flicker, lower brightness
A 2000 440 -100 60 0 0        # Audio Left: 440Hz tone, lower volume
A 2000 448 100 60 0 1         # Audio Right: 448Hz tone (creates 8Hz binaural beat)

# Test 3: Three simultaneous entries at t=5000ms
5000 12 30 50 1               # LED: 12Hz flicker, dimmer
A 5000 300 -100 50 0 0        # Audio Left: 300Hz tone
A 5000 312 100 50 0 1         # Audio Right: 312Hz tone (creates 12Hz binaural beat)

# Test 4: Mixed entry types at t=8000ms (LED + multiple audio channels)
8000 0 0 0 1                  # LED: Turn off
A 8000 0 0 0 0 0              # Audio Left: Fade out
A 8000 0 0 0 0 1              # Audio Right: Fade out

# Test 5: Single entry at t=10000ms (should work as before)
A 10000 500 0 30 0 0          # Single audio tone for comparison

# End test at t=12000ms
12000 0 0 0 1                 # LED off
A 12000 0 0 0 0 0             # Audio off